title: News24.com | Collen Maine nominated unopposed for ANCYL president
text: The ANC Youth League in KwaZulu-Natal has nominated North West chairperson Collen Maine as presidential candidate at the weekend. News24 3 days ago - World The North West ANC Youth League has nominated provincial chairperson Collen Maine as its presidential candidate for the upcoming national congress.
